  <p class="text-body"> After these quick user studies, I had to analyse the data to fill in the gaps. Here, putting myself in the user’s shoes and <strong>laying out a scenario</strong> in the form of a (wholly fictional and assumptive) story helped me open the project to a breadth of possibilities. </p>
